<html>
	<head>
		<title>NMBC_CARETPOSITION</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
	</head>
	<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
		<p><font color="#000000" size="4"><strong>NMBC_MARGINCLICK</strong></font></p>
		<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" width="100%" ID="Table1">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%" bgcolor="#e6e6e6"><pre>NMBC_MARGINCLICK<BR>
	lpnmsc = ( LPNMMARGINCLICKED )lParam;
</pre>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<p>
			Sent by the control when the user clicks inside one of the margins. This 
			notification message is sent in the form of a <strong>WM_NOTIFY</strong> message.</p>
		<ul>
			<LI>
				The return value is ignored by the control.
			</LI>
		</ul>
		<dl>
			<dt><em>lpnmsc</em>
				<dd>
					A pointer to a <a href="marginclick.htm">NMMARGINCLICK</a> structure which 
					contains the information about the position and margin in which was clicked.</dd>
		</dl>
	</body>
</html>
